{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778524326563,"sessionID":"ses_1e7b12db9ffef6WFKNReKFw6CU","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"chatcmpl-tool-85b32e9a6b8f0e34","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"__issue_context__.json"},"output":"<path>/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"**Preferred term label:**\\nocclusal surface of tooth\\n\\n**Synonyms**\\nchewing surface, masticatory surface\\n\\n**Definition (free text, please give PubMed ID)**\\nA tooth surface structure that forms the chewing edge of premolar or molar tooth. It functions chew or grind food during biting.\\nhttps://dentaleducationhub.com/surfaces-of-the-teeth/\\nhttps://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem-FDI-surface.html\\n\\n**Parent term (use https://www.ebi.ac.uk/ols/ontologies/uberon)**\\ntooth surface structure <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_8600148>\\n\\n**Your nano-attribution (ORCID)**\\nhttps://orcid.org/0000-0001-9625-1899\\nhttps://orcid.org/0009-0002-7282-0836\\n\\ncc @finn1928\\n\\n@aleixpuigb sorry we forgot to include this one as well\",\n3:   \"comments\": [\n4:     {\n5:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd87U3_ZQ\",\n6:       \"author\": {\n7:         \"login\": \"aleixpuigb\"\n8:       },\n9:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n10:       \"body\": \"Ok, I will add and make an Uberon release, there hasn't been one in a long time. Thanks!\",\n11:       \"createdAt\": \"2025-11-24T15:39:58Z\",\n12:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": true,\n13:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n14:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n15:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n16:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3631#issuecomment-3571447376\",\n17:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n18:     },\n19:     {\n20:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd87U4Cdi\",\n21:       \"author\": {\n22:         \"login\": \"aleixpuigb\"\n23:       },\n24:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n25:       \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please add this anatomical structure.\",\n26:       \"createdAt\": \"2025-11-24T15:42:49Z\",\n27:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n28:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n29:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n30:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n31:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3631#issuecomment-3571459938\",\n32:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n33:     }\n34:   ],\n35:   \"title\": \"NTR: occlusal surface of tooth\",\n36:   \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3631\"\n37: }\n\n(End of file - total 37 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"body\": \"**Preferred term label:**\\nocclusal surface of tooth\\n\\n**Synonyms**\\nchewing surface, masticatory surface\\n\\n**Definition (free text, please give PubMed ID)**\\nA tooth surface structure that forms the chewing edge of premolar or molar tooth. It functions chew or grind food during biting.\\nhttps://dentaleducationhub.com/surfaces-of-the-teeth/\\nhttps://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem-FDI-surface.html\\n\\n**Parent term (use https://www.ebi.ac.uk/ols/ontologies/uberon)**\\ntooth surface structure <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_8600148>\\n\\n**Your nano-attribution (ORCID)**\\nhttps://orcid.org/0000-0001-9625-1899\\nhttps://orcid.org/0009-0002-7282-0836\\n\\ncc @finn1928\\n\\n@aleixpuigb sorry we forgot to include this one as well\",\n  \"comments\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd87U3_ZQ\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"aleixpuigb\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n      \"body\": \"Ok, I will add and make an Uberon release, there hasn't been one in a long time. Thanks!\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2025-11-24T15:39:58Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": true,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reactionGroups\": [],\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3631#issuecomment-3571447376\",\n      \"viewe